    "In this approach, no data is centralized at any point, allowing participant businesses, endpoints, or edge devices to train machine learning models on their own data.",
    "The privacy of the network is protected because only model changes are shared instead of the original data.",
    "When it comes to protecting sensitive network information and staying in compliance with severe data privacy requirements, this cooperative technique shines 40.",
